rows.label: tlk45500421_03_msg0001
rows.name:
I wonder what'll be for dinner tonight...
Hohoh. As if I don't know the answer.

rows.label: tlk45500421_03_msg0002
rows.name:
I live together with my Blade partner,
you see, and she always serves up the
same thing every night.

rows.label: tlk45500421_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I can't complain, though. Decades I've
been eating them, and I still haven't
got sick of them! They're that good!
